{
  "texts": [
    "TDTs developmentA TDT model comprises three main components: a radiopharmacokinetic engine, a radiobiological optimizer, and an immunological modulator.",
    "In the following, we describe this model in detail.",
    "Radiopharmacokinetic engineThe main component of our model is a Physiologically Based RadioPharmacoKinetic (PBRPK) model, which can be constructed using mathematical, computational or AI-based approaches.",
    "This engine can be developed using physical, pharmacological, and physiological factors through patient data, including imaging, lab tests, and other clinical measurements.",
    "The PBRPK has multiple compartments, which are based on the total physiology of the human body."
  ]
}